	"description": "=== Essential Addons for Elementor ===\r Contributors: wpdevteam, Codetic, re_enter_rupok, Asif2BD, priyomukul, mahfuz01, nazsabuz\r Tags: elementor, elements, addons, elementor addon, elementor widget, page builder, builder, visual editor, wordpress page builder, elementor form\r Requires at least: 4.0\r Tested up to: 5.2\r Requires PHP: 5.4\r Stable tag: 3.3.0\r License: GPLv3\r License URI: https://opensource.org/licenses/GPL-3.0",
